## Don't Go To Font Jail

- Pale text: never for body. Use gray-600 minimum on white.
- Font weight 300: almost never. Use 400 minimum.
- Justified: avoid on the web.
- All-caps: labels only, never full paragraphs.
- Display fonts: headlines only.
- Line height: 1.6 minimum for all body text.
- Most problems come from prioritizing vibes over readability. Fix them before you ship.
